01:01.960 --> 01:03.880
How do I look?

01:03.880 --> 01:06.160
Oh, Jen, you look beautiful.

01:06.160 --> 01:07.720
All eyes are gonna be on you.

01:07.720 --> 01:09.840
I don't want to upstage the bride...

01:09.840 --> 01:11.080
much.

01:11.080 --> 01:13.040
Well, then,
don't stand at the front.

01:14.400 --> 01:16.560
Oh, wowzer!

01:16.560 --> 01:17.840
You look amazing!

01:20.200 --> 01:23.080
# The bells will ring

01:23.080 --> 01:25.400
# The sun will shine... #

01:25.400 --> 01:26.800
The car's here.

