All right, good.

01:28.960 --> 01:30.960
Are you nervous?
A little.

01:30.960 --> 01:32.880
Well, quite a lot, actually.

01:34.480 --> 01:35.880
I just don't want to let her down.

01:35.880 --> 01:37.640
